This product comes with full safety information and must be placed on a heatproof surface before use.

name: Fantasy LED Backflow Incense Burner - Purple Dragon
description:
Fantasy LED Backflow Incense Burner - Purple Dragon

Our range of backflow burners are made from resin and are for use with backflow incense cones only.

Backflow incense creates a mist when it is lit which flows down and around the backflow burner. This mist contains natural resins and oils that can create a light residue on the burner and surface around it which can be wiped clean with a damp cloth.

This product comes with full safety information and must be placed on a heatproof surface before use.

Our backflow burners are a great focal point in any room and are the perfect gift for any fantasy or gothic collector.

This item comes with 1 backflow incense cone included and required 2 AA batteries which are not included.

name: Backflow Incense Burner - Dragons Head
description:
Backflow Incense Burner - Dragons Head

Our range of backflow burners are made from resin and are for use with backflow incense cones only.

Backflow incense creates a mist when it is lit which flows down and around the backflow burner. This mist contains natural resins and oils that can create a light residue on the burner and surface around it which can be wiped clean with a damp cloth.

This product comes with full safety information and must be placed on a heatproof surface before use.

Our backflow burners are a great focal point in any room and are the perfect gift for any fantasy or gothic collector.

This item comes with 1 backflow incense cone included and a small foam mat to help protect the heatproof surface the burner is placed on.

Our range of backflow burners are made from resin and are for use with backflow incense cones only.

Backflow incense creates a mist when it is lit which flows down and around the backflow burner. This mist contains natural resins and oils that can create a light residue on the burner and surface around it which can be wiped clean with a damp cloth.

This product comes with full safety information and must be placed on a heatproof surface before use.

Our backflow burners are a great focal point in any room and are the perfect gift for any fantasy or gothic collector.

This item comes with 1 backflow incense cone included.
